Invocation Name: going the distance
des:
The companion Alexa skill to the Going the Distance Podcast on long distance relationships. 
Ask for ideas on date nights, text/quotes, or care packages to send to your remote significant other.
Admittedly simple right now, we plan to keep adding to make this a true resource to help you and your remote relationship person, go the distance.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
